{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e60f02c990","title":"对上海市革委会的号召","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"490b9ef5fc","index":0,"year":1967,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"e60f02c990","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1a25c11758","type":"title","text":"对上海市革委会的号台","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"e60f02c990","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"56ad98370f","type":"paragraph","text":"一、这次双方都有经验，这股风不会刮得很大，我们要遵守八条，解放军得遵守十条。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"e60f02c990","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ab2d14e07","type":"paragraph","text":"二、解放十几年来，我们脱离群众是很厉害的。青联、妇联、团中央都是空架子。我们的要求是不脱产，既当官，又当老百姓。有什么办法呢？一个月里当一个星期的官，三个星期的老百姓。假如不当老百姓，工人运动的领袖这样下去就可能变。这是个大方向问题。办法是否好，同志们可以提出来","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"e60f02c990","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":497,"end":497}},"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"117bb75f89","type":"paragraph","text":"一、这次双方都有经验，这股风不会刮得很大，我们要遵守《八条》，解放军得遵守《十条》。","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"e60f02c990","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1fca610fec","type":"paragraph","text":"二、解放十几年来，我们脱离群众是很厉害的。青联、妇联、团中央都是空架子。我们的要求是不脱产，既当官．又当老百姓。有什么办法呢？一个月里当一个星期的官，三个星期的老百姓。假如不当老百姓，工人运动的领袖这样下去就可能变。这是个大方向问题。办法是否好，同志们可以提出来。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"e60f02c990","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e67c92e72c","type":"title","text":"对上海市革委会的号召","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"e60f02c990","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":595,"end":595}}}},"__N_SSG":true}